  "description": "Choose from our fleet of premium party boats for your exclusive celebration: Day Tripper (14 people), Meeseeks and The Irony (18-25 people), or flagship Clever Girl (30-50 people) with giant Texas flag and 14 disco balls. Every private charter includes licensed captains, premium Bluetooth sound systems, large coolers with ice, and all the amenities for an unforgettable celebration. Perfect for weddings, corporate events, birthdays, and any special celebration. Starting at $200 per hour with a 4-hour minimum. Fully customizable packages to match your event needs.",
